        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2326920351" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12358666726871998790">I stole this book from my college, don’t worry I did pay for it, because I fell in love with the multitude of stories contained within. This book ended up inspiring me as a horror writer in my own right and gave me many hours of intense reading. If you can find this book it is worth not just the read but worth owning. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


