g (&quot;They&quot;), and H.G. Wells (&quot;Pollock and the Porroh Man&quot;). Included as well are such modern masters as Algernon Blackwood (&quot;Ancient Sorceries&quot;), Walter de la Mare (&quot;Out of the Deep&quot;), E.M. Forster (&quot;The Celestial Omnibus&quot;), Isak Dinesen (&quot;The Sailor-Boys Tale&quot;), H.P. Lovecraft (&quot;The Dunwich Horror&quot;), Dorothy L. Sayers (&quot;Suspicion&quot;), and Ernest Hemingway (&quot;The Killers&quot;). &quot;There is not a story in this collection that does not have the breath of life, achieve the full suspension of disbelief that is so particularly important in [this] type of fiction,&quot; wrote the Saturday Review. With an introduction and notes by Phyllis Cerf Wagner and Herbert Wise.<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"17564082537639735558\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'19_book_137763\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"BKAhH5pKllImn+TudqE1TjWrDyv8tqgQur28BTTZfL5G+Nk3NxSmuTKJ6sGMuvJtCPTpi0LppbnfEWro1WXC7g==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"137763\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"19_book_137763\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"existing_review\" id=\"existing_review\" value=\"false\" class=\"wtrExisting\" />\n<input type=\"hidden